pulses.name: 20250102 Most Active Threat Indicators
pulses.description:
02 Jan 2025 : Most Active Threat Indicators
#Cybersecurity #Cyberattack #RCE #Botnet #IOC

Top 3 Source Countries:

- United States (US) - The US is a major source of cyber activities, including multiple instances of SSH user authentication brute force attempts and various attacks exploiting Java Debug Wire Protocol vulnerabilities.
- China (CN) - China features prominently in cyber threats, particularly with numerous remote code execution exploits targeting DZS GPON and Dasan devices, as well as path traversal vulnerabilities in Apache HTTP servers.
- India (IN) - India shows a significant number of attacks, particularly involving SSH brute force attempts and multiple router command injections, indicating an active landscape for cyber exploitation.
